rvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));\n  }\n</style>","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/astrid/git/websites/meinblog/content/posts/ubuntu_docker-lamp/2ubuntu-git-einrichten.md","excerpt":"Ich verwalte meine Softwareprojekte mit Git. So greife ich jederzeit auf verschiedene Versionsstände zurück. Um die Dateien unkompliziert in…","fields":{"slug":"/ubuntu-git-einrichten-docker-lamp/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Git unter Ubuntu 20.04 einrichten","date":"03.02.2021","tags":["Linux","Ubuntu","Git"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":80,"height":80,"src":"/static/90020e3cb43b0bdf6641a85cf3dd7fea/829e2/ubuntu.png","srcSet":"/static/90020e3cb43b0bdf6641a85cf3dd7fea/829e2/ubuntu.png 1x,\n/static/90020e3cb43b0bdf6641a85cf3dd7fea/e94d6/ubuntu.png 1.5x"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/ubuntu-git-einrichten-docker-lamp/","previous":{"id":"ee8164d0-9b3f-56ee-900c-fdf8cd93d3c2","frontmatter":{"title":"Ubuntu 20.04, Docker, docker-lamp und Joomla Vorwort","tags":["Linux","Ubuntu"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/ubuntu-vorwort-docker-lamp/"}},"next":{"id":"e182c741-3aad-5fad-a2e7-a84a9e579a33","frontmatter":{"title":"Setting up Docker under Ubuntu 20.04","tags":["Linux","Ubuntu","Docker"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/en/ubuntu-docker-einrichten-docker-lamp/"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}